    "body": "If you're going to do this anyway, why not allow overriding the port? (e.g. pass port instead of dummy_port, to make it possible to override the rpcport)\r\n\r\nAfter all, the point of bracketed addresses is to allow `[ip]:port` specifications unambigiously.",
