    "body": "I chose not to allow overriding the port since we already have the `-rpcport` option, and this is the minimal functional change.\r\n\r\nI'm equally happy to make the one-line change so `-rpcconnect` can accept `<address>:<port>`. I have zero preference either way and I'm happy to go along with consensus opinion. @theuni has already expressed slight preference for allowing a port number in `-rpcconnect`.",
